This refactor improves:

### A. Cost

Less token usage than full-history prompting.

### B. Reliability

Less confusion from old or corrected statements.

### C. Engineering clarity

Every file has one job.

### D. Product fit

NeuroGPT is a symptom-seriousness pipeline, not a general assistant.

